text: Kurmanaybash () is a rural locality (a selo) in Miyakinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 194 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Kurmanaybash
